    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Baqir (AS), through the chain of Imam al-Sadiq (AS), identifies five occasions when supplication is especially potent and readily accepted: during Quran recitation, during the adhan, when rain is descending, when opposing armies meet on the battlefield for martyrdom, and when an oppressed person calls out to God. The final occasion is singled out with the remarkable statement that no barrier exists between such a supplication and God's Throne, underscoring the gravity of oppression and the divine guarantee of hearing the oppressed.",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "Du'a - supplication, calling upon God",
          "أذان": "Adhan - the Islamic call to prayer",
          "غيث": "Ghayth - rain, particularly beneficial rainfall",
          "مظلوم": "Mazlum - the oppressed, one who has been wronged",
          "عرش": "Arsh - the Throne of God"
        },
        "seo_question": "What are the five best times for supplication in Islam?"
      },
      "ur": {
        "summary": "امام باقر علیہ السلام نے پانچ مواقع بتائے جب دعا خاص طور پر قبول ہوتی ہے: قرآن کی تلاوت، اذان، بارش، جہاد اور مظلوم کی دعا۔",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "دعا - اللہ سے مانگنا",
          "مظلوم": "مظلوم - جس پر ظلم کیا گیا ہو"
        },
        "seo_question": "دعا کے قبول ہونے کے بہترین پانچ اوقات کون سے ہیں؟"
      },
      "tr": {
        "summary": "İmam Bâkır (a.s.), duanın özellikle kabul edildiği beş vakti belirtmiştir: Kur'ân tilaveti, ezan, yağmur, savaş ve mazlumun duası.",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "Dua - Allah'a yakarış",
          "مظلوم": "Mazlum - zulme uğramış kişi"
        },
        "seo_question": "İslam'da duanın kabul edildiği beş vakit nedir?"
      },
      "fa": {
        "summary": "امام باقر علیه السلام پنج موقعیت را بیان فرموده‌اند که دعا در آن‌ها به ویژه مستجاب می‌شود: تلاوت قرآن، اذان، بارش باران، نبرد و دعای مظلوم.",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "دعا - درخواست از خداوند",
          "مظلوم": "مظلوم - کسی که بر او ستم شده"
        },
        "seo_question": "بهترین پنج زمان برای دعا کردن کدام‌اند؟"
      },
      "id": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Baqir (AS) menyebutkan lima waktu ketika doa sangat dianjurkan dan mudah dikabulkan: saat membaca Al-Qur'an, adzan, hujan, pertempuran, dan doa orang teraniaya.",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "Doa - permohonan kepada Allah",
          "مظلوم": "Mazlum - orang yang dizalimi"
        },
        "seo_question": "Apa lima waktu terbaik untuk berdoa dalam Islam?"
      },
      "bn": {
        "summary": "ইমাম বাকির (আ.) পাঁচটি সময় চিহ্নিত করেছেন যখন দোয়া বিশেষভাবে কবুল হয়: কুরআন পাঠ, আযান, বৃষ্টি, যুদ্ধ এবং মজলুমের দোয়া।",
        "key_terms": {
          "دعاء": "দোয়া - আল্লাহর কাছে প্রার্থনা",
          "مظلوم": "মজলুম - নির্যাতিত ব্যক্তি"
        },
        "seo_question": "ইসলামে দোয়ার জন্য সেরা পাঁচটি সময় কোনগুলো?"
      },
      "es": {
        "summary": "El Imam al-Baqir (AS) identifica cinco momentos en los que la súplica es especialmente poderosa: durante la recitación del Corán, el adhan, la lluvia, la batalla y la súplica del oprimido.",
